Here's Part 6 of the GitHub-ready roadmap tables, rounding out the series with a Strategic Deployment Matrix. 
This segment maps certifications to their ideal use cases, governance relevance, and GitHub-ready deployment strategies—perfect for onboarding kits, sprint planners, or stakeholder documentation.

# 🧭 Strategic Certification Deployment Matrix

| **Track**           | **Certifications / Courses**                          | **Stakeholder Value**                          | **GitHub Deployment Strategy** |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------|
| Cybersecurity Core  | CCST, Security+, SC-900                                | Privacy, resilience, compliance                | Modular lab walkthroughs, badge tracker, sprint planner |
| Governance & Risk   | CISA, CISM, CISSP                                      | Risk, audit, boardroom trust                   | Governance glossary, ISO/NIST mapping, stakeholder Q&A sets |
| Responsible AI      | Microsoft, Google, IBM Responsible AI                 | Ethics, fairness, transparency                 | Ethical AI glossary, risk matrix, governance conversation starters |
| GenAI & Tooling     | AI-102, Coursera GenAI, GitHub Advanced Security      | Prompting, tooling, stakeholder fluency        | Prompting playbook, DevSecOps integration, sprint planner |
| Offensive Security  | OSCP, CEH, GPEN, CPTS                                  | Red team readiness, exploit development        | TryHackMe/HTB lab index, exploit walkthroughs, badge tracker |
| Defensive Security  | CySA+, CyberOps, Fortinet NSE                          | SOC operations, detection, incident response   | SIEM lab guides, SOC playbooks, threat response templates |
| Cloud & DevSecOps   | Azure Admin, GitHub Sec, Cloud+                        | Secure cloud deployment, CI/CD governance      | Cloud security modules, GitHub Pages integration, sprint planner |
| Entry-Level Onboarding | ITF+, Essentials Series, FreeCodeCamp              | Literacy, exposure, career exploration         | Reading plans, onboarding decks, GitHub starter kits |

